{"tid":1713706,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈 - 代言人","createTime":"2019-11-12T19:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T07:50:59.000Z","uid":52964,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b85552a6446174fde2f31c6dfc9b83e9d5e776c2","tid":1713706,"uid":52964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"From Wiki<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代言人</span></span></strong>（Product Endorser、Advertising Endorser），代替某方面發表言論的人。 也是指<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代表某一特定品牌、產品或服務</span></span></strong>，發表官方言論的人。 發言的目標是要達到正面的效果，例如令傳媒的觀眾對其代言的企業產生好感，投其信任的一票，或購買服務及商品等。<br />\n<br />\ne家既黃色經濟圈小弟覺得可以再發大啲<br />\n<br />\n如果一啲品牌搵代言既偽人係支持警暴，即係代表緊個品牌都係啦，何不罷買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵中國明星做代言人 （例子：楊冪）- 罷買<br />\n搵藍既偽人做代言 （例子：余文樂 - Bose; Jackson - 美心) - 罷買<br />\n搵護旗手做代言人 （例子：彭于晏 - Ctrip） - 罷買<br />\n搵無出聲既偽人做代言人 - 罷買<br />\n<br />\n當然調番轉，搵黃既藝人做代言就要努力懲罰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1056c8a6468d13262e85e22f1707a607dfbe3e56","tid":1713706,"uid":52964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"聽朝再推 <br />\n大家focus番係中大同聽朝既行動先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436293f3fc15298fcb060be948c44d7ff531cd44","tid":1713706,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:24:46.000Z","msg":"Tommy"},{"pid":"d422